Lady Hawk gave a royal smile and nod to Gotron, he didn't seem like the oth=
er Alliance bots she'd encountered. This one seemed more relaxed and laid b=
ack than the rest. He was sort of like Squizzy in manner. Thinking of Squiz=
zy she mentally kicked herself for not getting her away from the base.  She=
 had to learn who she could trust so she could do her work peacefully.

Lad=
y Hawk extended her hand palm down in a courtier style. She waited to see j=
ust how much class this bot had. "I'm humbled by your kind words my friend.=
" She kept her eyes on his movements, prepared for any conflicting interest=
s that might occur.
